https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Keys of the Kingdom
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Shaitan captures Gambit and uses him to open a portal to another dimension where an alien army is waiting to invade; Sage awakens Davis' latent mutant powers.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Beachhead !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: The forefront of Khan's Army begins its invasion of Earth, centering on Madripoor; Shaitan rescues Kahn from the X-Men; Storm is wounded and Kahn takes her back to his dimension to be his queen.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Second Front !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Kahn begins to woo Storm in hopes of making her his queen; The X-Folk prepare to rescue Gambit and take the battle to Kahn's realm.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Strikeback !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Rogue has Sage augment her powers so she can control all of the abilities she has ever absorbed; Heather transforms into her Shi'ar form; The X-Men begin their foray into Kahn's realm to rescue Storm and Gambit.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: All Or Nothing !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: The X-Men blast their way into Kahn's stronghold looking for Storm; Vargas confronts Rogue; Lifeguard evolves into a Shi'ar form; Storm is attacked by Kahn's harem who try to kill her for supplanting them as his chosen queen.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Final Gambit !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: Storm beats Kahn's harem back; Vargas reveals that he is going to try and kill Rogue because Destiny's Diary reveals that Rogue is going to kill him; Slipstream shunts Vargas into Kahn's stronghold where he starts wreaking havoc; The X-Men rescue Storm; Gambit begins to bring the house down.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: While I Live, You Don't Die !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: The X-Men halt Kahn's advance on the Earth and return from his dimension; Rogue and Gambit close the portal to Kahn's dimension, but while they are in a helpless position, Vargas stabs his sword through the both of them.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Rogue's Destiny: La Suerte De Matar !
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: After being stabbed through the heart last issue, Rogue begins to manifest the powers of many of the people she has touched over the years and decides to try and use this ability to take down Vargas.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Day of the Dead
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description: With the help of some fellow X-Men, the X-Treme team fight to recover from their dreadful injuries obtained in the war with Kahn; Davis is appalled by his sister's new Shi'ar appearance and leaves.

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Passages
